{{Quote|It's also a communications and justice issue. The Inrokini and Sabosen families handle those affairs, if my information is correct.|Luke Skywalker|<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Force Heretic I: Remnant">''[[The New Jedi Order: Force Heretic I: Remnant]]''</ref>}}
The '''Sabosen family''' (or '''House Sabosen''') was a [[Chiss/Legends|Chiss]] house, one of the [[Ruling Families/Legends|Ruling Families]] of the [[Chiss Ascendancy/Legends|Chiss Ascendancy]]. It was responsible for social issues such as justice, health, and education.

